SUMMARY:Covered Bridge Tour with Strasburg Scooter Tours
DESCRIPTION:There are some thrills of driving that you just don’t get cooped up in a car. Enjoy a guided covered bridge tour of Pennsylvania Dutch Country. Hop onto a 50cc scooter for a visit to a 19th century covered bridge with an experienced guide. \nThis tour offers exceptional views of the countryside\, including Amish farms and schoolhouses\, as well as an insightful look at one of Lancaster County’s oldest covered bridges. Enjoy miles of Amish country back roads to explore\, this tour will give you a uniquely exciting way to get back in touch with historic Pennsylvania. Looking for the perfect couples activity to complement this experience? Browse our list of unique date night ideas in Lancaster\, PA. \nItinerary\nDuration: 2 hours This tour includes: \n\nVisits and guided history of one of Lancaster’s oldest covered bridges\nAn expert introduction to the local Amish community\nDrives through Lancaster’s most beautiful\, undeveloped countryside\nAnd\, of course\, a few surprise stops along the way\nCovered Bridge Tours Monday through Saturday may make an additional visit to a private Amish homestead. Looking for fun activities for Sunday? Click here for things to do in Lancaster\, PA\, on a Sunday.\n\nAnd each trip is unique\, so you never know what we might have in store for you!
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/strasburg-scooter-tours-covered-bridge-tour/
LOCATION:Strasburg Scooter Tours\, 246 N Decatur Street\, Strasburg\, 17579\, United States
CATEGORIES:Children & Family events,Food & Beverage Events,Halloween,Labor Day,Memorial Day Weekend,Outdoor Activities,Strasburg, Pennsylvania,Tour
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Covered-Bridge-Tour.png
END:VEVENT
