SUMMARY:Country Roads Excursion with Strasburg Scooter Tours
DESCRIPTION:Experience Lancaster County in the 5-Star tour tradition of Strasburg Scooter Tours. Wind your way through back country roads\, on two or three wheels\, in search of our favorite Pennsylvania Dutch treats*\, off-the-beaten-path shops\, and special surprise encounters along the way. \nRide around farmland surrounding the Village of Intercourse and Bird-in-Hand\, PA. This tour is a great way to get up close and personal with Pennsylvania’s Amish Country while creating a lifetime of memories. \nItinerary\nDuration: Approximately 3 hours Our tours include: \n\nA convenient starting point in Strasburg\, PA\, right next to some of Lancaster well-loved destinations such as Sight & Sound\, Dutch Wonderland\, and American Music Theater\nA local expert guide will tour you through the heart of Amish farmland.\nBeautiful rolling farmscapes and off-the-beaten-path adventures\nEach trip is unique\, so you never know what we might have in store for you!\n\nThis is our best tour of Lancaster\, PA\, for kids! Adults love this tour (and have a blast even if they don’t have kids). \n*Unfortunately\, we regret to inform you that some of the food offerings on the tour may not be considered ‘Kosher.’ We apologize for any inconvenience.
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/strasburg-scooter-tours-country-roads-excursion-2/
LOCATION:Strasburg Scooter Tours\, 246 N Decatur Street\, Strasburg\, 17579\, United States
CATEGORIES:Children & Family events,Labor Day,Memorial Day Weekend,Outdoor Activities,Strasburg, Pennsylvania,Tour
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Country-Roads.png
END:VEVENT
