SUMMARY:Green Dragon Farmers Market
DESCRIPTION:Green Dragon Farmer’s Market: A True Lancaster County Experience!\nMillions of shoppers have visited this treasured Lancaster County Amish market since 1932! \nEnjoy a beautiful Friday morning at Lancaster’s favorite local farmer’s market! The Green Dragon Farmers Market & Auction sits humbly on a spacious 60-acre site in the heart of Amish Country. Since its inception in 1932\, we’ve grown to become one of the largest flea markets on the East Coast.
