SUMMARY:Jeff Foxworthy at American Music Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for a night of laughter with comedy legend Jeff Foxworthy — one of America’s best-loved stand-up stars. Foxworthy is the top-selling comedy-recording artist in history\, a multiple GRAMMY® nominee\, and the author of more than 26 books. He’s entertained audiences as the host of TV hits like Are You Smarter Than a 5th Grader? and appeared on NBC’s comedy competition series Bring the Funny. His comedy special “We’ve Been Thinking” is streaming on Netflix\, and he continues to headline tours across the country. \n\nCome Explore Our Lancaster Theaters and the Arts\n\n\nLive Theater\nLive Entertainment\nLive Music\n\n\n\nDinner Theaters\nMurder Mysteries\nThings To Do\n\n\n\nArtisan Collectives\nArt Galleries\nEvents Calendar
